snippet.title: ПИУ-ПИУ-БУМ! – Ранговые на Джинкс ➤ Стрим League of Legends
snippet.description:
Ссылка, по которой можно поддержать канал или заказать видео: https://www.donationalerts.com/r/dix0ntv

Напоминаю, что на канале (и стримах) есть возможность поддержать стримера и в благодарность получить видео или даже целый стрим на интересного вам чемпиона:
1. Игра на любом чемпионе (на стриме) – 200 руб.
2. Стрим на любого чемпиона (5-8 игр на протяжении 3-4 часов) – 1000 руб.
3. Обзор интересной и полной игры чемпиона на эло от Даймонда до Челленджера (стараюсь подбирать как можно более высокий ранг) – 300 руб.
4. Разбор определенного матч-апа в нескольких играх, как играют лучшие игроки против своих контр-пиков, например Кейл против Ирелии – 300 руб.

*Прошу обратить внимание на то, что не на всех чемпионах и не всегда получаются образцовые игры, но я очень стараюсь и пытаюсь каждую игру отыграть максимально хорошо.

► Основной игровой профиль (эло, статистика, сборки, история матчей и т.п.): https://www.leagueofgraphs.com/summoner/euw/SongOfMoon 
► Страница ВК: https://vk.com/dix0ntv 
► Поддержка канала (донат): https://www.donationalerts.com/r/dix0ntv 
► YouTube Dixon TV (Лига Легенд и стримы): https://www.youtube.com/c/DixonTV 
► YouTube Dixon Games (канал на английском): https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2LDOvKPvnGstkvz8TwdMyw/featured 
► YouTube Обсерватория Лиги Легенд: https://www.youtube.com/c/ОбсерваторияЛигиЛегенд
► Телеграм: https://t.me/Dixon_TV
► Группа Discord: https://discord.gg/SF8Jyjj
► Скачать игру Лига Легенд (League of Legends) с официального сайта: https://signup.ru.leagueoflegends.com/ru/signup/redownload
► Играю в Лигу Легенд с 2016 года на сервере EU-West. Менял роли, но сейчас закрепился на ТОПе. На данный момент около десяти брал Платину и один раз Даймонд
►Ссылка на регистрацию на сервере EU-West: https://play.euw.leagueoflegends.com/en_GB

ПОЛЕЗНЫЕ ВИДОСЫ:
1. Лучшие чемпионы для новичков: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vUXtAOSBPuM&t
2. Лучшие чемпионы для игры с плохим ПК или Интернетом: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2qLjUMExaNM
3. Сколько нужно фармить за игру: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WIgnmnCSIPg
4. Три способа просмотра реплеев: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JYkIUylW_Ac 
5. Позиционирование за Кейл и других чемпионов дальнего боя: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c2y3pEZh5yE
6. Главные советы для поднятия ранга: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PD7sFEXEBDs
7. Популярные ошибки, которые не дают повысить ранг в игре: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dxfw0hEF0iI 

ПРАВИЛА:
Канал рассчитан на взрослых и адекватных людей с целью создания приятного сообщества по общим интересам вокруг Лиги Легенд. Основное требование – никого не оскорблять и не выводить из себя. Так же просьба не спамить, не капсить и быть поаккуратней с критикой, когда плохо идет игра (не хочу, но могу чисто на тильте сорваться и влупить бан, особенно тем, кого прежде в чате не видел). 

Обсуждение религий, сексуальной ориентации, политики, войн и военных операций тоже крайне не приветствуются (просто во избежание превращения чата стрима в помойку из-за срача с оскорблениями между людьми с противоположными взглядами)! Вы все равно никому ничего не докажите и свое мнение тоже не измените, проверенно тысячами людей в миллионах подобных споров.

#Джинкс #DixonTV #лигалегенд #Jinx #диксонтв #leagueoflegends #guide #гайд

localizations.ru.description:
Ссылка, по которой можно поддержать канал или заказать видео: https://www.donationalerts.com/r/dix0ntv

Напоминаю, что на канале (и стримах) есть возможность поддержать стримера и в благодарность получить видео или даже целый стрим на интересного вам чемпиона:
1. Игра на любом чемпионе (на стриме) – 200 руб.
2. Стрим на любого чемпиона (5-8 игр на протяжении 3-4 часов) – 1000 руб.
3. Обзор интересной и полной игры чемпиона на эло от Даймонда до Челленджера (стараюсь подбирать как можно более высокий ранг) – 300 руб.
4. Разбор определенного матч-апа в нескольких играх, как играют лучшие игроки против своих контр-пиков, например Кейл против Ирелии – 300 руб.

*Прошу обратить внимание на то, что не на всех чемпионах и не всегда получаются образцовые игры, но я очень стараюсь и пытаюсь каждую игру отыграть максимально хорошо.

► Основной игровой профиль (эло, статистика, сборки, история матчей и т.п.): https://www.leagueofgraphs.com/summoner/euw/SongOfMoon 
► Страница ВК: https://vk.com/dix0ntv 
► Поддержка канала (донат): https://www.donationalerts.com/r/dix0ntv 
► YouTube Dixon TV (Лига Легенд и стримы): https://www.youtube.com/c/DixonTV 
► YouTube Dixon Games (канал на английском): https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2LDOvKPvnGstkvz8TwdMyw/featured 
► YouTube Обсерватория Лиги Легенд: https://www.youtube.com/c/ОбсерваторияЛигиЛегенд
► Телеграм: https://t.me/Dixon_TV
► Группа Discord: https://discord.gg/SF8Jyjj
► Скачать игру Лига Легенд (League of Legends) с официального сайта: https://signup.ru.leagueoflegends.com/ru/signup/redownload
► Играю в Лигу Легенд с 2016 года на сервере EU-West. Менял роли, но сейчас закрепился на ТОПе. На данный момент около десяти брал Платину и один раз Даймонд
►Ссылка на регистрацию на сервере EU-West: https://play.euw.leagueoflegends.com/en_GB

ПРАВИЛА:
Канал рассчитан на взрослых и адекватных людей с целью создания приятного сообщества по общим интересам вокруг Лиги Легенд. Основное требование – никого не оскорблять и не выводить из себя. Так же просьба не спамить, не капсить и быть поаккуратней с критикой, когда плохо идет игра (не хочу, но могу чисто на тильте сорваться и влупить бан, особенно тем, кого прежде в чате не видел).

Somos guerreros. La temporada 2020 ya comenzó. 

CRÉDITOS DE PRODUCCIÓN:

"Warriors"
Original de: Imagine Dragons
Artistas invitados: 2WEI y Edda Hayes
Producción: 2WEI
Voces: Edda Hayes
https://2wei.audio/

Video creado en colaboración con Blur Studio
http://www.blur.com/

Letra:

En tu niñez, esperabas
Y mirabas desde lejos
Pero siempre supiste que estarías trabajando
Mientras los demás jugaban
De joven, en vez
De dormir, planeabas
Todas las cosas que ibas a cambiar
¡Pero solo era un sueño!
Estamos aquí, no te rindas ahora
Somos los guerreros que erigieron esta ciudad
Estamos aquí, no te rindas ahora
Somos los guerreros que erigieron esta ciudad
Desde cero.
Estamos aquí, no te rindas ahora
Somos los guerreros que erigieron esta ciudad
Somos los guerreros que erigieron esta ciudad
Desde cero.

Lyrics:

As a child you would wait
And watch from far away
But you always knew that you'd be the one
That work while they all play
In youth you'd lay
Awake at night and scheme
Of all the things that you would change
But it was just a dream!
Here we are, don't turn away now,
We are the warriors that built this town
Here we are, don't turn away now
We are the warriors that built this town
From dust.
Here we are, don't turn away now,
We are the warriors that built this town
We are the warriors that built this town
From dust.

#leagueoflegends #warriors2020 #wearewarriors #somosguerreros

localizations.ja.title: Warriors (ft. 2WEI and Edda Hayes)│シーズン2020 シネマティック
localizations.ja.description:
Warriors 達の2020年が始まる。

クレジット：

"Warriors"
Original song by: Imagine Dragons
Featured artists: 2WEI and Edda Hayes
Produced by: 2WEI
Vocals performed by: Edda Hayes
https://2wei.audio/

ビデオ制作パートナー： Blur Studio
http://www.blur.com/

歌詞：

As a child you would wait
子供の頃はただ遠くから

And watch from far away
見ているだけだった

But you always knew that you'd be the one
だけど　いつか向こう側へ行くと信じて

That work while they all play
ひたすら努力していた

In youth you'd lay
若い頃は

Awake at night and scheme
ひたすら考えていた

Of all the things that you would change
夜も眠らず　自分に何が変えられるのか

But it was just a dream!
でも考えるだけなら夢にしかならない

Here we are, don't turn away now,
我々はこの場所にいる　逃げることなく

We are the warriors that built this town
我々は戦う　自分たちが創り上げたこの場所で

Here we are, don't turn away now
我々はこの場所にいる　逃げることなく

We are the warriors that built this town
我々は戦う　自分たちが創り上げたこの場所で

From dust.
かつては無かったこの場所で

Here we are, don't turn away now,
我々はこの場所にいる　逃げることなく

We are the warriors that built this town
我々は戦う　自分たちが創り上げたこの場所で

We are the warriors that built this town

From dust.

snippet.title: The Call | Season 2022 Cinematic - League of Legends (ft. 2WEI, Louis Leibfried, and Edda Hayes)
snippet.description:
For the fallen. For the deserted. For the downtrodden. And for those who will rise again. 

Season 2022 is here. How will you answer the Call?

Video created in partnership with Unit Image and Ben Hibon.

LISTEN NOW: https://found.ee/thecall 
Spotify: https://found.ee/thecall-spotify
Apple Music: https://found.ee/thecall-applemusic
Amazon Music: https://found.ee/thecall-amazonmusic
Youtube Music: https://found.ee/thecall-youtube
Deezer: https://found.ee/thecall-deezer


"The Call"

Featured artists: 2WEI, Louis Leibfried, and Edda Hayes
Written by: Louis „LoOF" Leibfried, Hermann Schepetkov, Christian Vorländer, Simon Heeger
Produced by: 2WEI & Mr. Herms
Mixed and Mastered by: 2WEI & Mr. Herms
Vocals performed by: Louis Leibfried and Edda Hayes
Additional vocals performed by: Colm McGuinness and SVRCINA
Executive Producer and Supervision by: Riot Music Team

​​2WEI: https://www.youtube.com/2WEIMUSIC
Louis Leibfried: https://open.spotify.com/artist/0t9nu4uUtGK24BUkWa5b4R?si=vQPIK6jZTkak5ylnJvfPvA
Edda Hayes: http://www.instagram.com/thisiseddahayes/


Lyrics:

Hear my plea to the fallen            
Leave me to be with the broken 
one last time before I go

Hold the last burning ember 
Let us never surrender
May we rise unto the Call
For the Glory and the Fall

For the beat and the broken
For the lost and forsaken
Let us never surrender
May we rise unto the Call

For the beat and the broken
For the lost and forsaken
Let us never surrender
For the Glory and the Fall

For the beat and the broken
For the lost and forsaken
Let us never surrender
Now we rise unto the Call

(For the beat and the broken)
Chains that we are breaking 
Fate that we are awaiting 
We will rise unto the Call
(Rise unto the Call)

For the Glory and the Fall


Read through the stories on Universe to learn more about each champion’s journey:

“Dead of Winter”
https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/story/dead-of-winter/

“The Faceless God”
https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/story/the-faceless-god/

“Hollowspun”
https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/story/hollowspun/

"In Battle, Broken"
https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/story/in-battle-broken/


League of Legends - Free Download & Play
https://signup.leagueoflegends.com/


#TheCall

製作名單：
Burn It All Down 
主唱: PVRIS
作詞: Riot Music Team and Alex Seaver of Mako
製作團隊: Riot Music Team 
混音團隊: Eric J and Riot Music Team
後製處理: Mike Bozzi at Bernie Grundman 
聲音演出: PVRIS 
音樂發行: Riot Music Team and Alex Seaver of Mako 
P/C Riot Games 2021

https://linktr.ee/thisispvris

MV製作: 與合作夥伴 Haoliners Animation 共同製作
http://haoliners.net

歌詞：
這並非傳說的起源
你也不像一個英雄
難道不能像朵嬌小的花兒一樣好好地坐下來玩嗎
就繼續說吧 就繼續笑吧
有一天你就會後悔
當所有人都想要變得火紅 火紅
或許是時候讓他們見證心中的龍

如果你想要控制住我
如果你想要把我隔絕在外
不讓我進入你的城牆
我將會讓你失去所有

因為我將會
燃盡 燃盡 燃盡一切
然後我們將會燃盡一切
就來看看這次誰會站到最後
而我將會
燃盡 燃盡 燃盡一切
讓我們將一切破壞殆盡
Bye bye bye
與火炎共舞 
我們會燃盡一切

這就是傷口的由來
這就是遊戲變得險惡的時刻
血液、汗水、眼淚從不停歇
輕舐著我的盤子因為我是如此飢渴
就繼續說吧 就繼續笑吧 
將來你就會知道後果
當所有人都想要變得火紅 火紅
是時候讓他們見證他們心中的龍

如果你想要控制住我
如果你想要把我隔絕在外
不讓我進入你的城牆
我將會讓你失去所有

因為我將會
燃盡 燃盡 燃盡一切
然後我們將會燃盡一切
就來看看這次誰會站到最後
而我將會
燃盡 燃盡 燃盡一切
讓我們將一切破壞殆盡
Bye bye bye
與火炎共舞 
我們會燃盡一切

從現在開始
你已經遭到包圍
不要再說大話
把你一切的質疑深埋進土裡
他們將會看著你踏過餘燼
現在是該我贏下回合的時刻

因為我將會
燃盡 燃盡 燃盡一切
然後我們將會燃盡一切
就來看看這次誰會站到最後
而我將會
燃盡 燃盡 燃盡一切
讓我們將一切破壞殆盡
Bye bye bye
與火炎共舞 
我們會燃盡一切

รายชื่อทีมโปรดักชั่น
Burn It All Down 
ศิลปินหลัก: PVRIS
เขียนบทโดย: Riot Music Team and Alex Seaver of Mako
ผลิตโดย: Riot Music Team 
มิกซ์โดย: Eric J and Riot Music Team
จัดทำโดย: Mike Bozzi at Bernie Grundman 
ร้องนำโดย: PVRIS 
ฝ่ายผลิตด้านเนื้อร้องโดย Riot Music Team และ Alex Seaver of Mako
P/C Riot Games 2021

https://linktr.ee/thisispvris

มิวสิกวิดีโอ: ผลิตและมีการร่วมมือโดย Haoliners Animation
http://haoliners.net

เนื้อร้อง

นี่ไม่ใช่สถานที่ที่เหล่าตำนานจากมา
เจ้าดูไม่เหมือนฮีโร่เลยสักนิด
ดอกไม้ดอกเล็กแสนสวยจะไม่ปล่อยให้เจ้านั่งอยู่เฉย ๆ หรอกนะ
พูดต่อไป หัวเราะร่าต่อไป
แล้วสักวันหวังว่าเจ้าจะไม่ได้ทำอีก
ทุกคนล้วนต้องการไฟ ไฟ
บางทีอาจจะได้เวลาพบกับมังกรแล้ว

ถ้าเจ้าอยากจะล้มข้า
แล้วเจ้าจะไม่ปล่อยให้ข้าเข้าไป
ในแดนดินหลังกำแพงปราสาท
พวกเจ้าไม่มีใครที่จะหยุดมันได้

เพราะตัวของข้านั้น
จักเผามันให้หมดสิ้น
ทุกอย่างจะถูกเผาจนหมดสิ้น
โอดูสิ มาดูว่าใครโดตขึ้นขึ้นจากเดิมกันบ้าง
และถ้าหากข้าต้อง
ต้องพังทุกอย่างให้ราบลง
ก็ให้มันพังซะให้หมด
บายบายบาย
เล่นกับไฟ
และเราจะเผาเจ้าให้เป็นจุล

และความบอบช้ำจะเกิดที่ตรงนั้น
และที่แห่งนั้นคือที่ทุกอย่างเลวร้ายลง
รอยเลือด หยาดเหงื่อและน้ำตาจะไหลหลั่ง
แม้แต่จานก็ต้องเลียจนแห้งเพราะข้าหิวเหลือเกิน
พูดต่อไป หัวเราะต่อไป
แล้วสักวันเจ้าจะรู้ว่าเกิดอะไรขึ้น
ทุกคนล้วนต้องการไฟ ไฟ
บางทีอาจจะได้เวลาพบกับมังกรแล้ว

ถ้าเจ้าอยากจะล้มข้า
แล้วเจ้าจะไม่ปล่อยให้ข้าเข้าไป
ในแดนดินหลังกำแพงปราสาท
พวกเจ้าไม่มีใครที่จะหยุดมันได้

เพราะตัวของข้านั้น
จักเผามันให้หมดสิ้น
ทุกอย่างจะถูกเผาจนหมดสิ้น
โอดูสิ มาดูว่าใครโดตขึ้นขึ้นจากเดิมกันบ้าง
และถ้าหากข้าต้อง
ต้องพังทุกอย่างให้ราบลง
ก็ให้มันพังซะให้หมด
บายบายบาย
เล่นกับไฟ
และเราจะเผาเจ้าให้เป็นจุล

มันเริ่มขึ้นแล้ว
ยาหยีเจ้าถูกล้อมไว้แล้ว
เอาเงินยัดใส่ปากของเจ้าไว้
ฝังความสงสัยไว้ใต้ผืนดิน
แล้วพวกมันจะมองเจ้าเดินเหยียบย้ำซากธุลี
และตอนนี้ ถึงเวลาที่ข้าจะเริ่มตาของข้าแล้ว

เพราะตัวของข้านั้น
จักเผามันให้หมดสิ้น
ทุกอย่างจะถูกเผาจนหมดสิ้น

League of Legends (LoL) is a multiplayer online battle arena video game developed and published by Riot Games for Microsoft Windows and macOS. The game follows a freemium model and is supported by microtransactions, and was inspired by the Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne mod, Defense of the Ancients.

In League of Legends, players assume the role of an unseen "summoner" that controls a "champion" with unique abilities and battle against a team of other players or computer-controlled champions. The goal is usually to destroy the opposing team's "Nexus", a structure that lies at the heart of a base protected by defensive structures, although other distinct game modes exist as well. 

Each League of Legends match is discrete, with all champions starting off relatively weak but increasing in strength by accumulating items and experience over the course of the game. The champions and setting blend a variety of elements, including high fantasy, steampunk, and Lovecraftian horror.

#LeagueOfLegends #LoLSeason2020 #LoLWarriors

“RISE”
Featured artists: The Glitch Mob, Mako, and The Word Alive
Written by: Riot Music Team and Alex Seaver of Mako

Welcome to the war we've only begun, so
Pick up your weapon and face it
There's blood on the crown go and take it
You get one shot to make it out alive, so
Higher and higher you chase it
It’s deep in your bones, go and take it
This is your moment, now is your time, so

Prove yourself and 
RISE, RISE
Make 'em remember you
RISE
Push through hell and 
RISE, RISE
They will remember you
RISE

Visions pray that one false step lead the end, so
Higher and higher you chase it
It's deep in your blood, go and take it
This is your moment, take to the skies, go

Prove yourself and 
RISE, RISE
Make 'em remember you
RISE
Push through hell and

They will remember you
RISE

Get along 'long get a move on up

Get along 'long get a move on up
And as you fight among the death beneath the dirt
Do you know yet?
Do you want it?
And when the giants call to ask you what you're worth
Do you know if,
Win or die, you'll

Prove yourself and 
RISE, RISE
Make 'em remember you
RISE
Push through hell and

They will remember you
RISE

snippet.title: K/DA - MORE ft. Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Ascend the throne. K/DA is back with “MORE,” featuring Madison Beer, SOYEON and MIYEON of (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, and Seraphine.

K/DA is a virtual music supergroup by Ahri, Evelynn, Akali, and Kai’Sa. Look out for their upcoming ALL OUT EP, releasing on November 6, 2020.

Follow @KDA_MUSIC on Twitter and Instagram for updates.

LISTEN NOW:

https://ffm.to/kdamore
Spotify: https://ffm.to/kdamore-spotify
Apple Music: https://ffm.to/kdamore-applemusic
YouTube Music: https://ffm.to/kdamore-youtubemusic
Deezer: https://ffm.to/kdamore-deezer
Amazon Music: https://ffm.to/kdamore-amazonmusic

PRODUCTION CREDITS:

K/DA - "MORE"
Featured artists: Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine 
Written by: Riot Music Team and Bekuh BOOM
Mandarin Chinese translation by: Lexie Liu and Yixuan Pang 
Korean translation by: Lydia Paek and Minji Kim
Produced by: Riot Music Team 
Executive produced by: K/DA and Seraphine 
Mixed by: Riot Music Team
Mastered by: Riot Music Team  
Vocals performed by: Madison Beer, SOYEON of (G)I-DLE, MIYEON of (G)I-DLE Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns
Additional vocals by: Bekuh BOOM
Vocal production by: Riot Music Team 
P/C Riot Games 2020

http://madisonbeer.com/
https://www.instagram.com/official_g_i_dle
https://www.instagram.com/lexieliu_
https://www.instagram.com/jairaburns
https://www.instagram.com/seradotwav
https://www.instagram.com/kda_music/

Music Video created in partnership with Axis Studios
https://axisstudiosgroup.com/

Madison Beer appears courtesy of Epic Records

Lyrics:

K/DA
Should we show 'em how we do it everyday
(na na na)
Let's get 'em

Akali that girl
Kali go grr
Kali don’t stop
Kali don’t skrr
Kali got a job
Kali go to work
뜨거워 언제나
Don’t get burnt
넘쳐흘러 more than a buffet
난 죽여 주잖아 like I’m Buffy
누가 감히 on my huffy
거- 문 열지 마 that's a rough day

I’m giving you more
Cause I’m greater than
필요 없는 시험들
답은 이미
But all of my numbers are talking babe
부루마블 mrs 모노폴리
너는 - 종이 돈이 나는 real money
필요 없대 너네들이 많은 돈들
Go get it go get it go get it the mission
눈을 못 떼 모두 그래 너도 그래
Cause I got it different

All I’ll ever know
Is life up on a throne
시작하면 끝을 보는 거야
You want

More
Know I got it
So here you go
You look like you could use some more
Know I got it
And never running low
Yeah I got

More than enough add it up and away
You know I got it like
Bomb bomb Blow your mind
Never giving less and that’s how it’ll stay
You know I got it like
All day, All the time

When I go it’s for gold
Yeah they cool but I’m cold
I don’t fit in the mold
I’m a rebel
I don’t do what you say
Making moves I don't wait
While I smile in your face
I got different DNA

What’s higher than the top
That’s me
Come take a look
Before falling at my feet
조용히 몸을 숙여봐
So take a look
나를 기억해 a queen

Way out
感觉犹如海浪
On the wave now
不断往前遨游
Never weighed down
就是我每天想要的模样
Wow

But I know I know
You want some more
我知道你
什么要求
But I know I know
You want some more
准备好就一起走
Giving it all

MORE RIOT GAMES MUSIC:

https://www.youtube.com/user/RiotGamesInc/playlists?shelf_id=23&sort=dd&view=50

PLAY LEAGUE OF LEGENDS:
http://riot.com/signup

snippet.title: LEAGUE OF LEGENDS - The Complete Cinematic Story Movie (2020) 4K ULTRA HD
snippet.description:
The Cinematic movie for League of Legends 2020 Season including all Cinematics and Cutscenes up to and including September 2020 pieced together to provide you with a seamless cinematic experience in 4K Ultra HD at 60 FPS.

League of Legends (LoL) is a multiplayer online battle arena video game developed and published by Riot Games for Microsoft Windows and macOS. The game follows a freemium model and is supported by microtransactions, and was inspired by the Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne mod, Defense of the Ancients.

In League of Legends, players assume the role of an unseen "summoner" that controls a "champion" with unique abilities and battle against a team of other players or computer-controlled champions. The goal is usually to destroy the opposing team's "Nexus", a structure that lies at the heart of a base protected by defensive structures, although other distinct game modes exist as well. 

GAMEPLAY
The game is played in three-dimensional isometric perspective, and consists of three primary game modes Summoner's Rift, and ARAM. Players compete in matches that usually last 20 to 50 minutes. In each game mode, teams work together to achieve a victory condition, typically destroying the core building (called the Nexus) in the enemy team's base after bypassing a line of defensive structures called turrets, or towers.

SETTING
League of Legends is independent from the extended lore of Runeterra, and is published through comics, short stories, and animated shorts.

League is the primary driver of the intellectual property's expanded universe, through champion releases and gameplay updates, which are accompanied with updated lore.[41] Given the nature of its development, Runeterra is made up of an assortment of genre staples, with regions and factions all possessing recognisable characteristics from wider popular culture. Cass Marshall of Polygon writes the lore is "a collection of genres ranging from Lovecraftian horror to knights and banners fantasy to pirate power struggles."

Demacia is a powerful region that values chivalry, with a medieval European aesthetic, and is known for the oppression of magic-users. Noxus is an empire ruled by a triumvirate, and is reminiscent of the Roman Empire, defined by its aggressive military aggression, expansionism, and high valuation of might. Piltover and Zaun are twin cities inspired by steampunk writing. Piltover, the city of progress, has a visual identity of gold and silver, and exploits the under-city of Zaun to maintain its rapid technological advancement. Zaun is depicted as dirty, with a green color identity, and its champions are often criminals or orphans. The Freljord is an ice-covered land in the north of Runeterra, where ancient, trapped horrors sleep beneath the ice while rival kingdoms fight in a civil war. Bandle City is the home of yordles, child-sized fae beings, and exists in the Spirit Realm, generally inaccessible to mortals. Yordles exist in most regions of Runeterra, and take on the traits of the region they belong to.

Ionia is not a formal nation, but a large archipelago inspired by Eastern mysticism, with monks and ninjas who wield spirit and shadow magic. Ionia is the primary residence of many Vastaya, animal-human hybrids with a strong connection to Ionia's natural magic. To the south of Ionia is Bilgewater, a port city in the Serpent Isles filled with pirates, bounty hunters, gamblers, and a sea monster fishing industry. South east of Bilgewater are the Shadow Isles, another archipelago which was corrupted by an ancient ritual gone wrong. A malign force known as the Black List permeates the isles, empowering undead beings.

Shurima is the largest continent of Runeterra, a vast desert and seat of an ancient empire until its destruction, is largely occupied by nomadic tribes. It is based on Ancient Egyptian mythology. Targon is a region which includes Mount Targon, the tallest peak in Runeterra, and a gateway to a realm occupied by celestial beings. It is reminiscent of Greek mythology. The Void, deeply inspired by Lovecraftian horror and the Cthulhu mythos, is a separate dimension populated by cosmic horrors, which enter Runeterra through portals.

snippet.localized.description:
The Cinematic movie for League of Legends 2020 Season including all Cinematics and Cutscenes up to and including September 2020 pieced together to provide you with a seamless cinematic experience in 4K Ultra HD at 60 FPS.

League of Legends (LoL) is a multiplayer online battle arena video game developed and published by Riot Games for Microsoft Windows and macOS. The game follows a freemium model and is supported by microtransactions, and was inspired by the Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne mod, Defense of the Ancients.

In League of Legends, players assume the role of an unseen "summoner" that controls a "champion" with unique abilities and battle against a team of other players or computer-controlled champions. The goal is usually to destroy the opposing team's "Nexus", a structure that lies at the heart of a base protected by defensive structures, although other distinct game modes exist as well. 

GAMEPLAY
The game is played in three-dimensional isometric perspective, and consists of three primary game modes Summoner's Rift, and ARAM. Players compete in matches that usually last 20 to 50 minutes. In each game mode, teams work together to achieve a victory condition, typically destroying the core building (called the Nexus) in the enemy team's base after bypassing a line of defensive structures called turrets, or towers.

SETTING
League of Legends is independent from the extended lore of Runeterra, and is published through comics, short stories, and animated shorts.

League is the primary driver of the intellectual property's expanded universe, through champion releases and gameplay updates, which are accompanied with updated lore.[41] Given the nature of its development, Runeterra is made up of an assortment of genre staples, with regions and factions all possessing recognisable characteristics from wider popular culture. Cass Marshall of Polygon writes the lore is "a collection of genres ranging from Lovecraftian horror to knights and banners fantasy to pirate power struggles."

Demacia is a powerful region that values chivalry, with a medieval European aesthetic, and is known for the oppression of magic-users. Noxus is an empire ruled by a triumvirate, and is reminiscent of the Roman Empire, defined by its aggressive military aggression, expansionism, and high valuation of might. Piltover and Zaun are twin cities inspired by steampunk writing. Piltover, the city of progress, has a visual identity of gold and silver, and exploits the under-city of Zaun to maintain its rapid technological advancement. Zaun is depicted as dirty, with a green color identity, and its champions are often criminals or orphans. The Freljord is an ice-covered land in the north of Runeterra, where ancient, trapped horrors sleep beneath the ice while rival kingdoms fight in a civil war. Bandle City is the home of yordles, child-sized fae beings, and exists in the Spirit Realm, generally inaccessible to mortals. Yordles exist in most regions of Runeterra, and take on the traits of the region they belong to.

Ionia is not a formal nation, but a large archipelago inspired by Eastern mysticism, with monks and ninjas who wield spirit and shadow magic. Ionia is the primary residence of many Vastaya, animal-human hybrids with a strong connection to Ionia's natural magic. To the south of Ionia is Bilgewater, a port city in the Serpent Isles filled with pirates, bounty hunters, gamblers, and a sea monster fishing industry. South east of Bilgewater are the Shadow Isles, another archipelago which was corrupted by an ancient ritual gone wrong. A malign force known as the Black List permeates the isles, empowering undead beings.

Shurima is the largest continent of Runeterra, a vast desert and seat of an ancient empire until its destruction, is largely occupied by nomadic tribes. It is based on Ancient Egyptian mythology. Targon is a region which includes Mount Targon, the tallest peak in Runeterra, and a gateway to a realm occupied by celestial beings. It is reminiscent of Greek mythology. The Void, deeply inspired by Lovecraftian horror and the Cthulhu mythos, is a separate dimension populated by cosmic horrors, which enter Runeterra through portals.

snippet.title: Imagine Dragons & JID - Enemy (from the series Arcane League of Legends) | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Oh, the misery, everybody wants to be my ENEMY. Watch the official music video for Arcane’s title track, Enemy. Arcane is coming to Netflix on November 6 at 7:00 PM PT.

PRODUCTION CREDITS
Enemy by Imagine Dragons & JID
Written by: Dan Reynolds, Wayne Sermon, Ben McKee, Daniel Platzman, Robin Fredriksson, Mattias Larsson, Justin Tranter, Destin Route p/k/a J.I.D
Produced by: Mattman & Robin (Wolf Cousins Productions)
Mixed by: Serban Ghenea (MixStar Studios)
Mastered by: Randy Merrill (Sterling Sound, NYC)
Session Engineer: Ben Sedano (Conway Studios), John Hanes

ANIMATION: 
Fortiche Prod
Co-Directors: Arnaud Delord, Bart Maunoury
Producers: Pascal Charrue, Jérôme Combe
Production Company: Fortiche, Riot Games


LYRICS
Look out for yourself!

I wake up to the sounds of the silence that allows
For my mind to run around, with my ear up to the ground
I’m searching to behold the stories that are told
When my back is to the world, that was smiling when I turned
Tell you you’re the greatest
But once you turn they hate us

Oh, the misery!
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Spare the sympathy
Everybody wants to be
My enemy... y... y... y...
Look out for yourself!
My enemy... y... y... y...
Look out for yourself!
But I’m ready

Your words up on the wall, as you’re praying for my fall
And the laughter in the halls, and the names that I’ve been called
I stack it in my mind, and I’m waiting for the time
When I show you what it’s like, to be words spit in a mic!
Tell you you’re the greatest
But once you turn they hate us

Oh, the misery!
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Spare the sympathy
Everybody wants to be 
My enemy... y... y... y...
Look out for yourself!
My enemy... y... y... y...
Look out for yourself!

Look, okay
I’m hoping that somebody pray for me
I’m praying that somebody hope for me
I’m staying where nobody ‘posed to be
P-p-posted
Being a wreck of emotions
Ready to go whenever just let me know
The road is long so put the pedal into the floor
The enemy’s on my trail, my energy unavailable
Imma tell ‘em hasta luego

They wanna plot on my trot to the top, 
I’ve been outta shape, thinkin’ out the box
I’m an astronaut, I blasted off the planet rock
To cause Catastrophe and it matters more because I had it not
Had I thought about wreaking havoc on an opposition
Kinda shockin’ they wanted static with precision
I’m automatic quarterback, I ain’t talkin’ sacking
Pack it, pack it up, Iont panic, batter batter up
Who the baddest, it don’t matter, cause we at ya throat

Everybody wants to be my enemy
Spare the sympathy
Everybody wants to be
My enemy
Oh, the misery!
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Spare the sympathy
Everybody wants to be 
My enemy

They say pray it away, I swear, I’ll never be a Saint, no way
My enemy
They say pray it away, I swear, I’ll never be a Saint

Look out for yourself!

From the Arcane: League of Legends Original Soundtrack
November 6 // November 13 // November 20
The #Arcane soundtrack drops in three releases. 
Pre-save now. https://lnk.to/ArcaneLeagueofLegends

localizations.pt-BR.description:

CRÉDITOS DA PRODUÇÃO
Enemy, de Imagine Dragons e JID

Minha mente em agitação, encosto os ouvidos no chão

Paralisado

Pronto para ir a qualquer lugar,

localizations.vi.description:
Oh, the misery, everybody wants to be my ENEMY. Hãy thưởng thức ngay Enemy - music video chính thức cho ca khúc chủ đề của Arcane. Arcane sẽ công chiếu trên Netflix vào 9h sáng ngày 07/11 (giờ Việt Nam).

ĐỘI NGŨ SẢN XUẤT
Bài hát Enemy của Imagine Dragons & JID
Sáng tác: Dan Reynolds, Wayne Sermon, Ben McKee, Daniel Platzman, Robin Fredriksson, Mattias Larsson, Justin Tranter, Destin Route còn được biết đến với cái tên J.I.D
Sản xuất: Mattman & Robin (Wolf Cousins Productions)
Phối nhạc: Serban Ghenea (MixStar Studios)
Chỉnh sửa & hoàn thiện (Mastering): Randy Merrill (Sterling Sound, NYC)
Chỉnh sửa thu âm: Ben Sedano (Conway Studios), John Hanes

HOẠT ẢNH: 
Fortiche Prod
Đồng đạo diễn: Arnaud Delord, Bart Maunoury
Nhà sản xuất: Pascal Charrue, Jérôme Combe
Công ty sản xuất: Fortiche, Riot Games


LỜI BÀI HÁT
Look out for yourself

I wake up to the sounds of the silence that allows
For my mind to run around, with my ear up to the ground
I’m searching to behold the stories that are told
When my back is to the world, that was smiling when I turned
Tell you you’re the greatest
But once you turn they hate us

Oh, the misery
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Spare the sympathy
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Look out for yourself
My enemy
Look out for yourself
But I’m ready

Your words up on the wall, as you’re praying for my fall
And the laughter in the halls, and the names that I’ve been called
I stack it in my mind, and I’m waiting for the time
When I show you what it’s like, to be words spit in a mic
Tell you you’re the greatest
But once you turn they hate us

Oh, the misery
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Smell the sympathy
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Look out for yourself
My enemy
Look, look, look, look, look out for yourself

Yeah
Uh, look, okay
I’m hoping that somebody pray for me
I’m praying that somebody hope for me
I’m staying where nobody ‘posed to be
P-p-posted
Being a wreck of emotions
Ready to go whenever just let me know
The road is long so put the pedal into the floor
The enemy’s on my trail
My energy unavailable
Imma tell ‘em hasta luego
They wanna plot on my trot to the top
I’ve been outta shape
Thinkin’ out the box
I’m an astronaut
I blasted off the planet rock to cause Catastrophe and it matters, more because I had it not,
Had I thought about wreaking havoc on an opposition
Kinda shockin’ they wanted static
With precision I’m automatic quarterback
I ain’t talkin’ sacking
Pack it pack it up
I don’t panic
Batter batter up
Who the baddest
It don’t matter
Cause we at ya throat

Everybody wants to be my enemy
Spare the sympathy
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Oh, the misery
Everybody wants to be my enemy
Spare the sympathy
Everybody wants to be my enemy

They say pray it away, I swear, I’ll never be a Saint, no way
My enemy
They say pray it away, I swear, I’ll never be a Saint
Look out for yourself

Từ nhạc phim Arcane: Liên Minh Huyền Thoại
Ngày 07 tháng 11 // Ngày 13 tháng 11 // Ngày 20 tháng 11
Nhạc phim #Arcane sẽ được phát hành trong 3 đợt. 
Đừng bỏ lỡ.[ĐƯỜNG DẪN]

P/C năm 2020 bởi Darkroom/Interscope Records với giấy phép độc quyền thuộc Tập đoàn Riot Games.                                                                                              Cùng sự tham gia của Imagine Dragons với sự đồng thuận từ KIDinaKORNER/Interscope Records.                                                                                                                                                     Cùng sự tham gia của JID với sự đồng thuận từ Dreamville/Interscope Records

snippet.title: Awaken | Season 2019 Cinematic - League of Legends (ft. Valerie Broussard)
snippet.description:
A deadly masterpiece unfolds.  A lone resistance made whole. A chance to come alive.

Season 2019 has begun - why will you fight?

LISTEN NOW:
Spotify: http://smarturl.it/awakenlol/spotify
Apple Music: http://smarturl.it/awakenlol/applemusic
iTunes: http://smarturl.it/awakenlol/itunes
GooglePlay: http://smarturl.it/awakenlol/googleplay
Deezer: http://smarturl.it/awakenlol/deezer

Click for more music videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UOxkGD8qRB4&list=PLbAFXJC0J5Gbogs-3Jk3nay0sAeAqi3SS 

A New Dawn (Cinematic): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vzHrjOMfHPY 
A Twist of Fate (Cinematic): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tEnsqpThaFg 

"Awaken"

Featured artist: Valerie Broussard
Featured violinist: Ray Chen
Written by: Riot Music Team and Alex Seaver of Mako
Produced by: Riot Music Team and Alex Seaver of Mako
Mixed and mastered by: Riot Music Team
Vocals performed by: Valerie Broussard
Violin performed by: Ray Chen
Vocal production by: Riot Music Team, Alex Seaver of Mako, and AG

https://www.valeriebroussardmusic.com/ 
https://www.raychenviolin.com/

ANIMATION:
Digic Pictures

LYRICS:
The night beckons while you dream
A life never lives in peace

As you stand upon the edge, woven by a single thread
And fate may fall down upon you
While the devil is knocking, right at your door

So all you restless, each night you hear the drums of war
Awaken, Awaken
The voice begins to call you while you hunger
A taste of destiny you're searching for
Awaken, Awaken
The fight is at your door so take up the cause

Awaken (repeats)

As you stand upon the edge, hanging in the balance
And fate may fall down upon you
While the devil is knocking
So all you restless, each night you hear the drums of war

Awaken, Awaken
The voice begins to call you while you hunger
A taste of destiny you're searching for

Awaken, Awaken
Awaken
